# OpenClaw Prometheus 指标定义

> 版本：v0.2.9 | 更新：2026-04-20
> 遵循 [Prometheus 命名规范](https://prometheus.io/docs/practices/naming/) 与 [Grafana 最佳实践](https://grafana.com/docs/grafana/latest/fundamentals/exemplars/)

---

## 设计原则

1. **命名**：`openclaw_{subsystem}_{metric}_{unit}`，单位后缀统一（`_seconds`、`_bytes`、`_total`、`_total`）
2. **类型**：counter 用 `_total` 后缀；gauge 无后缀；histogram/summary 用 `_seconds`/`_bytes`
3. **标签**：低基数优先；`channel`、`provider`、`model`、`agent_id`、`tool` 为常用分组维度
4. **Grafana 友好**：每个指标族都有对应的 PromQL 模板和推荐面板类型

---

## 1. Exporter 元数据（Plugin Meta）

| 指标 | 类型 | 说明 |
|------|------|------|
| `openclaw_exporter_build_info` | gauge | 插件版本信息，labels: `plugin`, `version`。Grafana 用 `group_left` 做 enrich |
| `openclaw_metrics_last_scrape_duration_seconds` | gauge | 最近一次采集耗时 |
| `openclaw_metrics_collector_success` | gauge | 采集器健康，labels: `collector`。1=成功 0=失败 |
| `openclaw_metrics_collect_errors_total` | counter | 采集器累计失败次数，labels: `collector` |
| `openclaw_metrics_http_requests_total` | counter | HTTP 端点请求计数，labels: `route`, `method`, `status` |
| HTTP 端点延迟 | histogram | `route`, `method` | 支持 `histogram_quantile` 跨实例聚合 |
| `openclaw_gateway_operator_rpc_requests_total` | counter | Gateway RPC 调用计数，labels: `method` |
| `openclaw_plugin_uptime_seconds` | gauge | 插件运行时长 |
| `openclaw_plugin_hook_invocations_total` | counter | Hook 调用次数，labels: `hook` |

**Grafana 面板建议**：
- Stat Panel：`openclaw_exporter_build_info` 显示版本
- Time series：`rate(openclaw_metrics_http_requests_total[5m])` 按 route 分组
- Stat：`openclaw_metrics_last_scrape_duration_seconds` 监控采集性能

---

## 2. Gateway 健康（Health RPC）

来源：`health` RPC

| 指标 | 类型 | 标签 | 说明 |
|------|------|------|------|
| `openclaw_up` | gauge | - | Gateway 健康 1=ok 0=error |
| `openclaw_health_check_duration_seconds` | gauge | - | 健康检查耗时（秒） |
| `openclaw_uptime_seconds` | gauge | - | Gateway 运行时长 |
| `openclaw_heartbeat_interval_seconds` | gauge | - | 心跳间隔 |
| `openclaw_agents_configured_total` | gauge | - | 已配置 agent 数量 |
| `openclaw_sessions_count` | gauge | - | 会话总数（health 快照） |
| `openclaw_channels_total` | gauge | - | 渠道总数 |
| `openclaw_channels_linked_total` | gauge | - | 已链接渠道数 |
| `openclaw_channel_linked` | gauge | `channel_id`, `channel_label` | 单渠道链接状态 0/1 |

**Grafana 面板建议**：
- **Stat**：`openclaw_up` → 绿/红
- **Gauge**：`openclaw_agents_configured_total`
- **Bar gauge**：`openclaw_channel_linked` 按 channel_id 分组

---

## 3. 渠道（Channels RPC）

来源：`channels.status` RPC

| 指标 | 类型 | 标签 | 说明 |
|------|------|------|------|
| `openclaw_channel_total` | gauge | - | 配置渠道总数 |
| `openclaw_channel_linked_total` | gauge | - | 已链接渠道数 |
| `openclaw_channel_unlinked_total` | gauge | - | 未链接渠道数 |
| `openclaw_channel_linked` | gauge | `channel_id`, `channel_type`, `channel_label` | 单渠道链接状态 |
| `openclaw_channel_accounts` | gauge | `channel_id` | 每渠道账号数 |
| `openclaw_channel_last_event_timestamp_seconds` | gauge | `channel`, `account` | 最近事件时间戳 |
| `openclaw_channel_last_inbound_age_seconds` | gauge | `channel`, `account` | 最近入站消息距今秒数 |
| `openclaw_channel_last_outbound_age_seconds` | gauge | `channel`, `account` | 最近出站消息距今秒数 |
| `openclaw_channel_failures_total` | counter | `channel`, `reason` | 渠道发送失败数 |

**Grafana 面板建议**：
- **Table**：`openclaw_channel_linked` + `openclaw_channel_accounts` → 渠道状态一览
- **Time series**：`time() - openclaw_channel_last_event_timestamp_seconds` → 渠道活跃度

